					<p>&#8220;I have highlighted that contrary evidence exists, not because I have attempted to equate it to evidence to the contrary, only because Ms Raff‚Äôs post on several occasions says that no evidence to the contrary exists and goes through the mock exercise of referencing articles to support this claim.&#8221;</p>
