	<li class="comment byuser comment-author-kmcrober odd alt depth-9 clearfix highlander-comment" id="li-comment-48977">
		<div class="comment-container">
							<div class="avatar-holder">
					<img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8fab9113a1a4503b1ac32eb1d3461ccb?s=50&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-50' height='50' width='50' />
