				<div class="comment-head">
					<span class="name"><a href='http://www.violentmetaphors.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Colin</a></span>
											<span class="date"><a href="http://violentmetaphors.com/2014/03/25/parents-you-are-being-lied-to/comment-page-15/#comment-49760" title="Permalink">July 31, 2014 at 8:19 pm</a></span>
						<span class="edit"></span>
