				<div class="comment-head">
					<span class="name">Chris</span>
											<span class="date"><a href="http://violentmetaphors.com/2014/03/25/parents-you-are-being-lied-to/comment-page-15/#comment-64317" title="Permalink">September 23, 2014 at 3:39 pm</a></span>
